song_name: Amazon Let This Be A Voice

version_description: I was going for simple, yet perfection when I figured out these chords and when to play them.
Written to be fingerpicked on acoustic guitar. Starts in C, transposes to D. Capo 4 for vocal range change.

song_name: Baby You Look Good To Me Tonight

version_description: The chords are best on this version and the words are correct.  In my review of other contributions, I couldn't find one that had both the correct chords and lyrics.  In addition, the format of this submission is far easier to play, especially around a campfire.
